title: What to do AFTER you over-eat
itunes:title: What to do AFTER you over-eat
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

You just had a big ole overeat and you feel like crap physically and emotionally.

Overeating can not only leave you with a full belly, it can leave you with shame and regret. The feelings can be intense and can lead to actions that create a spiral of overeating and negative self-talk.

In today's podcast we take a look at how to determine why we overeat and strategize ways to stop the cycle of overeating.
